  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `v2.33.1`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\n#### Details\r\n\r\nRecently my Erigon node started to lag 10-15 blocks behind the tip of the chain for short periods of time, and I noticed these logs correlate with the lag spikes.\r\n\r\n```\r\n[WARN] [03-17|23:35:14.338] [Sentinel] fail to decode gossip packet  err=\"incorrect size\" topic=/eth2/4a26c58b/beacon_block/ssz_snappy pkt=*cltypes.SignedBeaconBlockBellatrix\r\n```\r\n\r\nI was unable to find more information about this log. I also noticed that there have been several releases since 2.33.1, would upgrading help here?\r\n\r\nThanks!\r\n\r\n",
